Summary: Unknown object caught on video near the moon
divs: sighting detailsi was alone lying on the outer edge of the concrete car pad located behind my house facing east. the moon and a star were visible, the star being slightly below the moon to the right. i was filming the moon. i bought the camera in august which is an hd jvc everio with a 200x digital zoom to shoot the video. i video taped something very odd which i posted on u-tube. link: www.youtube.com\watch?v=rlfscew_vd8 i thought someone from mufon should see this. i wish to keep my personal information confidential. information submitted by: debbie ziegelmeyer missouri mufon state director
